data.text: James Stewart Tait was born on 22 April 1839, in Stranorlar, County Donegal, Ireland. He had at least 1 son and 2 daughters with Ann Gracey. He lived in Philadelphia, Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, United States in 1880. He registered for military service in 1862. He died on 28 March 1915, in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, United States, at the age of 75, and was buried in West Laurel Hill, Lower Merion Township, Montgomery, Pennsylvania, United States.
